Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.19,0:00:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.27,0:00:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面我們開始執行搜索並生擒鼬的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.05,0:00:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曉的目的是收集尾獸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.44,0:00:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三尾很有可能已經落入他們的手中了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.77,0:00:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據自來也大人的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.72,0:00:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們盯上了鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.41,0:00:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此時已經進入了火之國也不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.93,0:00:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別是鼬出身於木葉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.98,0:00:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三年前為抓鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.99,0:00:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經潛入了村子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.35,0:00:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次也可以認為他會因此而瞄準木葉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.74,0:00:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為了抓到宇智波鼬 佐助也會…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.68,0:00:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要找到佐助的下落
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.99,0:00:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先別著急
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.80,0:00:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一步一步來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.99,0:01:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在說明一下搜索步驟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.41,0:01:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之以這裡為中心點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.09,0:01:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搜索周邊半徑五公里內的範圍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.19,0:01:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有收穫 則返回中心點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.32,0:01:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後從新的中心點搜索半徑五公里內的範圍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.28,0:01:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣反覆進行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.87,0:01:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五公里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.72,0:01:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼遠的話 無線電不就無法使用了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.91,0:01:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且獨自走那麼遠的話太過危險
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.36,0:01:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搜索隊伍原則上至少兩人一組
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.82,0:01:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到敵人的時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.73,0:01:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.80,0:01:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要那麼著急
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.61,0:01:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.91,0:01:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等的聲音皆比無線電傳得更遠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.92,0:01:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼻子也能及早察覺危險 並加以援助
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.49,0:01:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕克
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.16,0:01:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.92,0:01:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來說明一下搜索隊的編成方式
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.19,0:02:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為確保安全 此次每人帶兩隻忍犬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.97,0:02:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩隻 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.06,0:02:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以跟它們好好相處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.76,0:02:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教 小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.80,0:02:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你總是喜歡挑囉嗦的雌性呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.84,0:02:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟著志乃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟲子味臭死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.79,0:02:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狗味臭死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.59,0:02:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.88,0:02:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 好好相處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.35,0:02:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能和睦相處就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.18,0:02:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該能跟狗交上朋友的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.50,0:02:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.48,0:02:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人是人柱力 而且又被盯上了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.17,0:02:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考慮到可能會遭受襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.30,0:02:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跟大和及感知系的雛田一起行動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.66,0:02:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有大嗓門的布魯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.22,0:02:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請…請多指教 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.59,0:02:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 作為訓犬師的我和牙各帶一隻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.48,0:02:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就準備完畢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.48,0:03:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好 各位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.78,0:03:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優先追蹤鼬和佐助這兩人的氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.57,0:03:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論發現哪一方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.35,0:03:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待掌握他們的方位後
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.58,0:03:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就先回中心點來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.39,0:03:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別是鳴人 別太過衝動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.48,0:03:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.83,0:03:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了 出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.17,0:03:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.53,0:05:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們就出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.84,0:05:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇智波鼬嗎 能順利找到就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.29,0:05:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.73,0:05:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.73,0:05:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和佐助兩人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.61,0:05:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.02,0:05:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來已經沒問題了 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.74,0:06:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼要去哪邊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.05,0:06:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助還是九尾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.17,0:06:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 選哪一邊好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.34,0:06:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…迪達拉前輩 等等我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.31,0:06:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.63,0:06:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找小嘍囉好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.03,0:06:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去看看情況
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.87,0:06:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.28,0:07:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是曉的…叫啥來著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.68,0:07:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,角…角田…角斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.64,0:07:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,角都…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.41,0:07:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.17,0:07:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是那個角都手下的帳房先生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.75,0:07:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼都招
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.33,0:07:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請饒我一命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.07,0:07:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就全招了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.89,0:07:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就問問你們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.27,0:07:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤丸 可別輸給其它忍犬了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.78,0:07:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要在別人之前發現鼬和佐助的氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.56,0:08:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了 志乃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.86,0:08:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼慢慢吞吞的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.40,0:08:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟲子們不喜歡這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.45,0:08:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上了哦 斑點 小玉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.53,0:08:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斑點…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.97,0:08:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小玉…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.96,0:08:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要隨便給我們起外號啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.67,0:08:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.85,0:08:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擺出這麼一副母老虎的姿態
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.62,0:08:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人都會被你給嚇跑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.66,0:08:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.00,0:08:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雄性你越是追他跑得越快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.73,0:09:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是個窮追不捨的雌性吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.50,0:09:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻若不行就試試守吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.67,0:09:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說莫名其妙的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.88,0:09:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和佐助才不是那麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.32,0:09:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你這張嘴啊 還是那麼沒口德
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.80,0:09:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想把我和大家想說的話告訴佐助…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.04,0:09:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴他 大家都在等他回去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.49,0:09:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅此而已…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.97,0:09:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守也不行的話就讓我聞聞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.51,0:09:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.63,0:09:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很微弱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.79,0:09:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是隱約能夠聞到宇智波佐助的氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.97,0:09:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.35,0:09:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.28,0:09:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氣味不太明顯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.27,0:09:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過正在漸漸靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.16,0:10:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想幹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.82,0:10:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別弄得我們在發現他之前就暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.92,0:10:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心謹慎些
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.90,0:10:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很接近了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.30,0:10:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.64,0:10:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道附近沒發現佐助嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.13,0:11:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.57,0:11:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氣味遠離了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.17,0:11:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這車水馬龍的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.85,0:11:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也未察覺到異樣的查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.77,0:11:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是回佐助身邊去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.87,0:11:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正那兩人應該還沒回來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.90,0:11:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了 阿飛 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.58,0:11:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎 好快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.62,0:11:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪一邊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.97,0:12:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九尾還是佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.47,0:12:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是撿了個大便宜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.53,0:12:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該我們倆上了 阿飛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.33,0:12:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都問你是哪一邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.17,0:12:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.49,0:12:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 雛田 感覺到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.08,0:12:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.38,0:12:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我出來 什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.25,0:13:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是暴露了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.66,0:13:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藥師兜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.55,0:13:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到你會親自送上門來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.36,0:13:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有膽量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.16,0:13:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想跟鳴人談談而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.11,0:13:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次不會再讓你逃走了 一定要抓住你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.34,0:13:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兜 你肯定知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.26,0:13:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助的去向
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.23,0:13:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是老樣子 滿嘴佐助佐助的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.14,0:13:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助幹掉了大蛇丸 當真有此事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.18,0:13:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確有此事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.42,0:13:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.09,0:13:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我給鳴人帶了件禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.94,0:13:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那身裝束 你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.22,0:13:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是佐助嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.17,0:13:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然跟鼬長得很像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.68,0:13:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.24,0:14:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.34,0:14:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.18,0:14:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是以前我們組織所收集的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.96,0:14:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於曉的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.55,0:14:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼把這東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.60,0:14:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白送給你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.57,0:14:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在沒有大蛇丸當靠山的現今
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.65,0:14:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想用這個和木葉做交易嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.93,0:14:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 用這東西來做交易也太沒誠意了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.45,0:14:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別是跟木葉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.01,0:14:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼到底為何
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.95,0:14:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和大蛇丸不同
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.89,0:14:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並未被曉追殺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.00,0:14:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了感謝鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.77,0:14:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是份禮物而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.66,0:14:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,況且你被曉給盯上了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.38,0:14:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.92,0:14:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蛇丸大人死後
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.80,0:15:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又變得無法定位自己的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.35,0:15:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道父母是誰 也不知道所屬國家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.44,0:15:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於自小被敵人撿走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.52,0:15:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並以間諜身份來往各國各村的我而言
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.12,0:15:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國家和村子只是些曖昧的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.42,0:15:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到我成為大蛇丸大人的部下後
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.73,0:15:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…再一次消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.91,0:15:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己到底是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.41,0:15:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有身份的這種痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.86,0:15:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你應該能夠理解吧 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.14,0:15:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所說的我怎麼會理解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.62,0:15:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.57,0:15:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己是漩渦鳴人呢 還是九尾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.19,0:15:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經遭受過他人冷漠的視線
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.23,0:15:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也會懷疑自己到底是什麼東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.26,0:15:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你相信自己的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.02,0:15:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認定自己是漩渦鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.71,0:16:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堅強地承受了他人視你為九尾的目光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.93,0:16:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人到底想對鳴人幹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.21,0:16:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不知道他葫蘆裡賣的是什麼藥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.44,0:16:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你才會清楚地明白自己的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.47,0:16:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也結交了認可你的夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.74,0:16:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我從未想過要超越大蛇丸大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.99,0:16:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一味地追隨著他的那份力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.27,0:16:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的我 真的非常理解你的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.96,0:16:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你讓我有所覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.01,0:16:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我也想像你那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.70,0:16:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以這次…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.13,0:16:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要超越融入我體內的大蛇丸大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.59,0:16:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到全新且強大的自我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.96,0:16:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到全新的自我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.73,0:17:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你給我的啟發
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.90,0:17:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才要感謝你啊 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.19,0:17:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蛇丸大人是再生的象徵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.19,0:17:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他會成為我必須要超越的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.07,0:17:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我體內繼續存活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.70,0:17:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說融合嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.31,0:17:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.70,0:17:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是將被佐助打倒的大蛇丸大人遺體上的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.87,0:17:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,移植到這副身體上來而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.36,0:17:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這真是非常驚人的生命力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.79,0:17:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的身體反而被漸漸侵蝕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.57,0:17:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.70,0:17:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的行為
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.23,0:17:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.68,0:17:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白眼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.13,0:17:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體的三成已經被侵蝕了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.33,0:17:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不被吞噬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.32,0:17:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拚命地抵抗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.47,0:17:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能感覺到一個想要超越大蛇丸大人的自我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.34,0:18:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想說的只有這些嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.54,0:18:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就好好努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.76,0:18:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是在木葉的監獄裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.20,0:18:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木遁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.27,0:18:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 抓到他了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.11,0:18:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.28,0:18:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.42,0:18:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待我能完全控制大蛇丸大人的力量後
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.82,0:18:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會認真跟你過招的 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.51,0:18:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你還要等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.45,0:18:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是打倒大蛇丸大人的佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.23,0:18:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想對佐助幹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.66,0:18:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後會有期了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.79,0:19:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了 打倒佐助了 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.35,0:19:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是前輩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.61,0:19:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.64,0:19:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.06,0:19:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來略微有些本事呢 這個人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.21,0:19:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到大蛇丸居然會被這種小鬼幹掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.71,0:19:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是現在 我也無法相信 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.31,0:19:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們被一雙不錯的眼睛給盯上了 阿飛 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.91,0:19:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹勁十足嘛 前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.82,0:19:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後必須得向鼬道歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.44,0:21:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集火影忍者疾風傳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.07,0:21:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激突
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.31,0:21:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪達拉與佐助之戰終於開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.58,0:21:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在爆炸的襲擊中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.15,0:21:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助的命運又會如何…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.99,0:21:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四次忍界大戰爆發
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.43,0:22:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥席捲了風之國
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.74,0:22:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在鳴人的面前 我愛羅出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.88,0:22:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不想犧牲任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.20,0:22:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賭上守護之物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.73,0:22:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人的激戰開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.99,0:22:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劇場版火影忍者疾風傳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.80,0:22:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火之意志的繼承者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.05,0:22:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手大人每個月的還款期又到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.58,0:22:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豚豚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.60,0:22:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 就幹一場好久沒做的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.58,0:22:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼在這種地方睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.15,0:22:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會感冒的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.76,0:22:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼疼疼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.69,0:22:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.49,0:22:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我想借些錢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.86,0:22:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥 這可是件高檔品啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.03,0:22:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.19,0:23:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賣掉的話 大概值一百萬兩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.31,0:23:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 大姐 五十萬兩怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.90,0:23:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.33,0:23:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.74,0:23:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥 那隻豬不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.72,0:23:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 今天是何等地倒霉啊
